# Design System Rules for Dashboard Build

## üéØ CORE PRINCIPLE
When creating NEW components from scratch, use the integrated design system with semantic tokens. Existing dashboard components remain unchanged.

## üé® DESIGN SYSTEM USAGE

### Colors (Use Semantic Tokens)
```tsx
