className="text-primary bg-subtle border-primary"
className="text-brand bg-brand-subtle"
className="text-success bg-success-subtle"

// ‚ùå AVOID - Hard-coded colors for new components
className="text-gray-900 bg-gray-100"
className="text-blue-600 bg-blue-50"
```

### Typography (Use Design System Scale)
```tsx
// ‚úÖ CORRECT - Use semantic typography
className="text-h1 text-primary"     // Page titles
className="text-h2 text-primary"     // Section titles  
className="text-h3 text-primary"     // Subsections
className="text-h4 text-primary"     // Card titles
className="text-body text-secondary" // Body text
className="text-label text-primary"  // Form labels
className="text-caption text-tertiary" // Captions

// ‚ùå AVOID - Custom font sizes for new components
className="text-lg text-xl text-2xl"
```

### Spacing (Use Design System Scale)
```tsx
// ‚úÖ CORRECT - Use semantic spacing
className="p-4 m-2 gap-3"  // Uses design system scale
className="space-y-4"      // Consistent spacing

// ‚ùå AVOID - Arbitrary spacing for new components
className="p-[17px] m-[23px]"
```

### Shadows & Effects
```tsx
// ‚úÖ CORRECT - Use design system shadows
className="shadow shadow-md shadow-lg"
className="shadow-focus"           // Focus states
className="shadow-focus-success"   // Success focus
className="shadow-focus-warning"   // Warning focus
className="shadow-focus-error"     // Error focus
```

### Border Radius
```tsx
